match.name: SPARC January 31st
match.about:
Cam Cisneros will be the MD and has designed the course of fire for this match. Below are some notes from Cam:

Very fast paced shooting accessible targets for beginners to advanced. The name of the game for this match will be to have fun and hit targets. A hot Lunch provided after with sodas and water.  Fire pits  to warm your mitts.

Gate opens at 8 am
Zero starts at 8:15 am
Stage brief at 9 am
Stages hot at 9:30 am
